results.name: Number of ordered septuples of distinct pairwise coprime positive integers with largest element n.
link: Alois P. Heinz, Table of n, a(n) for n = 13..200
example: a(16) = 2 because there are 2 ordered septuples of distinct pairwise coprime positive integers with largest element 16: (1,3,5,7,11,13,16), (1,5,7,9,11,13,16).
